Comparing the 7-day averages of daily confirmed cases from the past 7 days and those from 8-14 days ago, case counts have increased by 2.9%, while daily reported deaths have decreased by 2.6%. Similar comparative 7-day averages in the USA show 0.76% increase in daily reported cases and 13.2% increase in reported deaths.

Impression: The global daily reported over 400 000 newly confirmed infections in the past 24 hours with over 251.04 million cumulative reported cases and over 5.07 million reported deaths. - Mod.UBA]
